{"tid":1763793,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"75m追隻小醜 真係痢狗先做得到","createTime":"2019-11-30T15:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T09:35:30.000Z","uid":137406,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"5870b530754ff4a0f6f672ce583fdedba2f91fc8","tid":1763793,"uid":137406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"睇住呢種柒真係令人心頭一振<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n季初洗横手搞鳩人，搞到要公海道歉，已經柒一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n季中幾條廢鳩連横自爆，又柒一鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果迫住唔屌又屌75m高追隻荷蘭狗，柒第三獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見班痢狗早兩個禮拜 J到天昏地暗，以為咩球王君臨咁巴閉啦，屌你老母一睇，嘩，水撚到吖，我以為睇緊學界啊75m 鐵衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一隊波可以由上至下都柒到咁勻循、咁立體、咁不堪入目，仲要自以為係一線班霸，世上真係得一隊臭痢狗做得到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/538208/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/538208/page/1?post=1</a>"},{"pid":"3842ccc6b970c358c844001d3fedc02b27962cc1","tid":1763793,"uid":64484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90af90e27e495e1f4edb9e95c690f88ddb0ba26","tid":1763793,"uid":174940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9034413f1086f725705037f652abdb0535552631","tid":1763793,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3deef22d6f0fa7ae8081cd899543e743e63450","tid":1763793,"uid":31398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15